Title: DockTab Framework for WPF
Description: A WPF docking framework (like Visual Studio or Expression Blend) with a strong focus on ease of use and performance. It provides DockTabControl that arranges it child DockTabItem and a windowing system that allows you to drag, drop and dock items between windows.

Project Description
A WPF docking framework (like Visual Studio or Expression Blend) with a strong focus on ease of use and performance. It provides DockTabControl that arranges it child DockTabItem and a windowing system that allows you to drag, drop and dock items between windows.

We are still in very early development state. Absolutely nothing is working yet.
